Returns the index within this string of the first occurrence of the specified substring. The returned index is the smallest value k for which: this.startsWith(str, k) If no such value of k exists, then -1 is returned. Params: str – the substring to search for. Returns: the index of the first occurrence of the specified substring, or -1 if there is no such occurrence.
